434
00:37:57,008 --> 00:37:58,475
No lo sé.

435
00:38:00,645 --> 00:38:02,738
Umibozu, ven un momento.

436
00:38:08,819 --> 00:38:10,286
¿Qué quieres?

437
00:38:10,688 --> 00:38:13,057
